接口 GiraphReader<T>

  • 类型参数:

    所有超级接口:

extends Iterator<T>
    Reader for some kind of data.

      • initialize

        void initialize(org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputSplit inputSplit,
              org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.TaskAttemptContext context)
                throws IOException,
                       InterruptedException
        Use the input split and context to setup reading. Guaranteed to be called prior to any other function.
        参数:
        inputSplit - Input split to be used for reading.
        context - Context from the task.
        抛出:
        IOException
        InterruptedException

      • getProgress

        float getProgress()
                  throws IOException,
                         InterruptedException
        How much of the input has the GiraphReader consumed i.e. has been processed by?
        返回:
        Progress from 0.0 to 1.0.
        抛出:
        IOException
        InterruptedException
